lyrics:
Stable Diffusion is the future of creation
With text and image you can make videos
No limits, no rules, just your vision
You are the master of your own illusion

Stable Diffusion is not just a game
It is a power that you have to use
But be careful what you show
Because not everything is as it seems

Stable Diffusion, Stable Diffusion
Change the world with your solution
Stable Diffusion, Stable Diffusion
Be ready for the revolution
